cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.LG, cs.CY

The paper discusses Named Entity Recognition (NER) in a historical Finnish newspaper collection using rule-based and semantic tagging tools. This falls under the sub-category of Natural Language Processing (NLP) which is covered by cs.CL. The paper also involves search and classification of entities, which can be related to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Deep Learning (cs.DL). The use of tools and evaluation of their performance can be related to Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
